<DOCUMENT source-infobase-name="Rules" content-collection-id="NYCrules" source-infobase-title="The Rules of the City of New York" base-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\" default-split-level="Chapter" makefile-filename="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\NYCrules.mak" css-stylesheet-href="#!-- #ID=NYCrules_css_id --#" xml-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCrules\output\HUCCVLERTKEUARDR\XML\" css-stylesheet-name="NYCrules_css" makefile-document-depth="2">
	<LEVEL style-name="Chapter" style-name-escaped="Chapter" style-id="0-0-0-477" level-depth="2" toc-section="false">
		<RECORD id="0-0-0-129510" number="67977" version="2027">
			<HEADING>Chapter 58: Housing Portal</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17142" name="T28C058"/>Chapter 58: Housing Portal</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-480" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Subtitle" style-name-escaped="Subtitle" style-id="0-0-0-15301" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-483" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Subpart" style-name-escaped="Subpart" style-id="0-0-0-15960" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-129100" number="67978" version="2017">
								<HEADING>§ 58-01 Definitions.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17144" name="T28C058_58-01"/>§ 58-01 Definitions.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129105" number="67979" version="2017">
									<PARA>As used in this chapter, the following terms have the following meanings. Capitalized terms not specifically defined in this chapter have the meanings set forth in the Act. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129129" number="67980" version="2306">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Act.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Act&quot; means <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Inter Infobase Jump" destination-infobase-id="671734137-329684122-0-0" destination-infobase-uil="L:\NY\New York City\Folio\Working\Admin.nfo" destination-infobase-name="" destination-infobase-title="" destination-name="T26C018" destination-id="0-0-0-0">Chapter 18 of Title 26</LINK> of the Administrative Code of the City of New York, as may be amended. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129128" number="67981" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Credible Complaint.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Credible Complaint&quot; means a complaint alleging that an owner has violated any provision of the Act with respect to an Affordable Unit that the Department has determined to be credible in accordance with subdivision (a) of 28 RCNY § <LINK style-name="Jump" style-name-escaped="Jump" style-id="0-0-0-31" type="Jump" destination-name="T28C058_58-05" destination-id="0-0-0-17152">58-05</LINK>. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129127" number="67982" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Unit Information.</CHARFORMAT> &quot;Unit Information&quot; shall mean any combination of Full Unit Information, Limited Unit Information, or Offered Unit Information. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129126" number="67983" version="2017">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 6/21/2021, eff. 7/21/2021) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-129133" number="67984" version="2017">
								<HEADING>§ 58-02 Marketing.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17146" name="T28C058_58-02"/>§ 58-02 Marketing.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129125" number="67985" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>An Affordable Unit that is offered for rent or sale through the Housing Portal must be offered for rent or sale exclusively through the Housing Portal. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129124" number="67986" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>An Affordable Unit that is offered for rent or sale through the Housing Portal must be rented or sold pursuant to such marketing guidelines as may be published by the Department. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129123" number="67987" version="2017">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 6/21/2021, eff. 7/21/2021) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-129132" number="67988" version="2017">
								<HEADING>§ 58-03 Unit Information.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17148" name="T28C058_58-03"/>§ 58-03 Unit Information.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129122" number="67989" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>In addition to the information specifically enumerated in the Act, the term &quot;Full Unit Information&quot; must also include the following information: <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129121" number="67990" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(1)<TAB tab-count="1"/>the name of any lawful leaseholder or owner of such unit, or lawful owner of shares of a cooperative corporation that entitle the shareholder to occupancy of such unit under a proprietary lease; <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129120" number="67991" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(2)<TAB tab-count="1"/>a statement as to the reason for turnover of such unit, if applicable; and <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129119" number="67992" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(3)<TAB tab-count="1"/>the household size of such unit. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129118" number="67993" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Limited Unit Information shall not include any of the information required by subdivision (a) of this section. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129117" number="67994" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(c)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Full Unit Information and Offered Unit Information must be submitted under penalty of perjury with a sworn statement by the owner that such information is in compliance with all applicable regulatory agreements and legal requirements. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129116" number="67995" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(d)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Full Unit Information and Offered Unit Information must be submitted to the Department through the Housing Portal, or through such alternative software application that interfaces with the Housing Portal as the Department will designate. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129115" number="67996" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(e)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Full Unit Information must be submitted to the Department no less than annually. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129114" number="67997" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(f)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Offered Unit Information must be submitted immediately upon the owner becoming aware of such unit&apos;s anticipated vacancy date. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129113" number="67998" version="2017">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 6/21/2021, eff. 7/21/2021) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-129131" number="67999" version="2017">
								<HEADING>§ 58-04 Lawful Leaseholder or Owner Verification.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17150" name="T28C058_58-04"/>§ 58-04 Lawful Leaseholder or Owner Verification.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129112" number="68000" version="2017">
									<PARA>In order to verify that a Housing Portal user is the lawful leaseholder or owner of an Affordable Unit, or is a lawful owner of shares of a cooperative corporation that entitle the shareholder to occupancy of an Affordable Unit under a proprietary lease, such user must complete the designated form provided by the Department on the Housing Portal and attach a copy of the lease, deed, or any other substantiating documentation. The Department will exercise its discretion in determining whether a Housing Portal user has satisfied this verification requirement. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129111" number="68001" version="2017">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 6/21/2021, eff. 7/21/2021) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
						<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-486" level-depth="7" toc-section="true">
							<RECORD id="0-0-0-129130" number="68002" version="2017">
								<HEADING>§ 58-05 Violations.</HEADING>
								<PARA>
									<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-17152" name="T28C058_58-05"/>§ 58-05 Violations.</PARA>
							</RECORD>
							<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129109" number="68003" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Credibility determinations.</CHARFORMAT> The Department will determine the credibility of complaints alleging that an owner has violated any provision of the Act with respect to an Affordable Unit. In determining the credibility of such complaints, the Department will consider any accompanying documentation attesting that an owner has violated any provision of the Act, corroborating testimony or any additional information the Department deems relevant. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129108" number="68004" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<CHARFORMAT bold="0" italic="1" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Verification of allegations.</CHARFORMAT>&#160;<HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129107" number="68005" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(1)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The Department will conduct an investigation of any Credible Complaint. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129106" number="68006" version="2017">
									<PARA>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>
										<TAB tab-count="1"/>(2)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Upon the completion of the investigation of a Credible Complaint, the Department will determine whether there is reasonable cause to believe a violation of the provisions of the Act or of this chapter have occurred. <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
								<RECORD id="0-0-0-129104" number="68007" version="2265">
									<PARA>(Added City Record 6/21/2021, eff. 7/21/2021) <HIGHLIGHTER style="highlighter-ALP" original-style-name="ALP" style-name-escaped="highlighter-ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-33">[ALP S-063]</HIGHLIGHTER>
									</PARA>
								</RECORD>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
	</LEVEL>
</DOCUMENT>